{"tid":1690733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃大仙有市民拍攝警車被警員截查","createTime":"2019-11-03T12:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T12:13:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dacfc603317872f452d568e5d9d1e089deada0df","tid":1690733,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1489838_1_20191103194827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1489838_1_20191103194827.jpg&h=a921b3f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民下午發起7區「行街」活動反對警暴，警方加強佈防。入夜後，黃大仙附近一帶仍有20名防暴警員戒備，期間有拍攝警車的市民被截查。<br />\n<br />\n晚上約7時，該名經過黃大仙前往食飯地點的市民表示，自己只是拍下停泊的警車，便被警方用電筒以白色強光照射，他因受驚嚇而用粗口責駡警察，其後數十名防暴警察衝向並包圍他，問他爲何要責罵他，又反用粗口責罵他。<br />\n<br />\n其後防暴警員檢查他身份證、搜身及背包，又要求他解鎖手機，證實自己是去吃飯後獲放行。<br />\n<br />\n較早時，防暴警察及多輛警車於黃大仙廣場戒備，又在附近一帶截查及搜查市民的背包。"},{"pid":"74e65a682476b087c98f3310f449141092c2fba8","tid":1690733,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489838-20191103.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489838-20191103.htm&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=ae77dfba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489838-20191103.htm&h=533c4cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489838-20191103.htm</a>"},{"pid":"68c045fc3375a4670dc1aca4db0469c108f812ef","tid":1690733,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"唔夠打就走講真唔好覺得羞恥<br />\n面對你打唔贏嘅對手無謂挑釁佢哋"},{"pid":"4374fb56106b322e7ba8598d22f4752390f595ad","tid":1690733,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68c045fc3375a4670dc1aca4db0469c108f812ef","tid":1690733,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:11:22.000Z","msg":"唔夠打就走講真唔好覺得羞恥<br />\n面對你打唔贏嘅對手無謂挑釁佢哋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:13:12.000Z","msg":"你話我係失敗撚都係咁講<br />\n對家宜家做乜都冇後果<br />\n一時嘅口舌之勇佢唔毛都唔會甩一條<br />\n你就俾人打到仆街"}]}